						               													<description>BreakScore - An iconic board game full of twists and turns, electrifying highs and heart-rendering crash and burns, that's great fun for board, dice and card game players, young and old alike! This is a major risk and reward game where much depends on the dice, the cards and the fickle finger of fate. No two games are ever the same ... and there is a mighty end twist that ensures that no game is over ... until it's absolutely over! ~ ideal for 2-4 game players / ages 10-adult / playing time approx 20-45 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Also included in the BreakScore game case are two bonus games;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Champ-Play - Absorbing to master, this no holds barred board game is highly recommended for cunning and competitive game players who excel at pushing their luck without going too far. Champ-Play can be pulsating and nerve-wracking ... definitely not for the faint-hearted! ~ ideal for 2-4 game players / ages 15-adult / playing time approx 20-45 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Break-Away - A race 'n' chase board game designed as the perfect lead-in to BreakScore. Easy to learn and quick to play, this is an unpredictable, non-repetitive game that can produce nail-biting finishes. It also encourages creative problem solving, rewards positive play and sharpens decision-making skills. ~ ideal for 2-4 game players / ages 7-adult / playing time approx 10-20 minutes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
